  "short_description": "Wi-Fi 6/6E USB adapter, 2.4 GHz / 5 GHz / 6 GHz, Bluetooth v5.2",
  "description": "The AWUS036AXM is a high-performance USB adapter that supports the latest Wi-Fi 6E standard. It features three bands: 2.4 GHz, 5 GHz, and 6 GHz, with a combined data transfer rate of up to 3000 Mbps. This makes it ideal for gaming online or downloading large files. AWUS036AXM has a built-in Bluetooth v5.2 antenna, so you can connect to your favorite Bluetooth devices, such as headphones and speakers. Bluetooth v5.2 provides higher-quality audio over Bluetooth, so you can enjoy your music and movies without any lag or interference. The USB adapter equipped with two RP-SMA external antenna connectors, so you can attach high-gain antennas to extend the range of your Wi-Fi signal. It also comes with two detachable dipole antennas, which are suitable for most use cases. The AWUS036AXM is easy to install and use. Simply plug it into an appropriate USB port on your computer and enjoy the benefits of Wi-Fi 6E.",
